{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when you saw the, the thing that really struck me was when they run into the ghetto, when everybody is running in all directions yelling and screaming, and it's total chaos, and you don't know what is happening.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, this is what was happening outside the window of the house we were in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this was a one-story shack like all of them, but the entrance to it was sort of through the alley and around the back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there was also a front entrance, which was a different part of the house, a different apartment where different people lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Somehow or other, they were emptying that section of the ghetto completely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were taking everybody out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were going from house to house, from apartment to apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They never got to the one where we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we could hear the boots of the sentries walking in the street outside the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't dare turn on the light.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were, sitting through the night, not knowing if there was anybody left alive in the entire ghetto, whether anybody was ever coming back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was happening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where did they take the people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Knowing that if we go out, who knows?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It might be good thing, or they might immediately kill us or what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We sat there through the night, not daring to move, not daring to talk, not daring to have any food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the longest night of my life more than likely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in the morning, around 10:00 in the morning, all of a sudden there was a great deal of noise.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard footsteps, and some of the people were coming back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And apparently they had taken everybody out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
